Interface Showable<T extends javafx.fxml.Initializable>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - any class that implements in Initializable interface
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ADBConnectionController, CreateBatchController, CreateFilterController, GetTouchPositionController, LogCatTabController, MonitorTabController

    public interface Showable<T extends javafx.fxml.Initializable>
    Any class that implements this interface can pop out of the main GUI, usually through the click of a button on it's parent controller
    Author:
    Ronan Watkins
